modName: Calling Shadowfax - A New Type of Whistle
descriptionHtml:
Ezio\'s Horse whistle sound V 1.0
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

A  replacer sound  for DarkenDe\'s Horse Whistle mod. Im a Tolkien maniac and i think you will love put that whistle. in your game  I made that by myself.

Quality : 320 kbps
Frequency : 97 db

Installing :
___________________________________________________________________________________________


-> Extract manually \"whistle.wav\" into your \"data/sound/fx\" folder

OR

-> Use Nexus Mod Manager


Uninstall
___________________________________________________________________


->Simply delete \"whistle.wav\" placed in \"data/sound/fx\"

OR

-> Use Nexus Mod Manager




*Thanks to DarkenDe for the original mod

>> mod : http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=5528
